QuestData.Title: Deterrent
QuestData.Description: General Jakra'zet had orders to ensure dis place had protection. Guard protection. I see none of dat.$b$bJakra'zet is a stubborn general, and one I have had my eye on for a while now.$b$bRegardless, we must remind dese lesser tribes who rules dis city with a message dey will understand.$b$bI charge you with collecting heads.$b$bEnter Tal'farrak and Tal'aman, and collect a quota of heads.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa Amani Heads from Tal'aman and $2oa Sandfury Heads from Tal'farrak.
